Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: 7,742 SF Freestanding Truck Repair Facility 1.5 km from 401 with 2.5 acres of yard available for lease. Located in Puslinch, ON at Exit 299 off of the 401, 15 min to Milton. Suitable for a 40 truck and 60 trailer operation. IND Zoning uses include contractors yard, body shop, fuel depot, transport terminal, manufacturing and trucking facility. Site is on a well and septic. Building offers in floor heating in the shop area and fully functional pits. CTPAT yard. Building is fully furnished complete with IT, phone system, office furniture and security system (22 cameras). Multiple options available including leasing the building and entire yard or multiple configurations of outdoor storage area. Both long and short term options available. Taxes: $2,721.00/per month.

Building well maintained and in good condition. 600amp/ 600 volt power, 3- 8' x 10' docks, 5 - 14' x 14' drive-in doors, 18'clear height. Yard is fully fenced, lit, gated entry, and graded.
